The Centre for Creative Arts (UKZN) and eThekwini Municipality is currently hosting the 21st JOMBA! Contemporary Dance Experience at various venues around the city, until 8 September. Showing the strength and beauty of male dancers, #BoysDanceToo is sharing the strong message against bullying, mocking and teasing of boys. It also encourages boys who wish to pursue their passion in dance, to fly  and capture that dream. The glorious annual dance showcase, Shall We Dance,Â will take place in the Playhouse Opera from 6 to 17 September.